### .gitignore

Create a file named `.gitignore` in your project root with the following content to ignore temporary and environment-specific files:

```gitignore
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/
ENV/

# Environment files
.env

# SQLite database files (adjust if you want to track these)
anilist_data.db
anilist_global.db
checkpoint.txt

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
embeddings_cache.pkl
anime_vectors.index